Tarak is a professional foley artist whose     
obsession with creating sound effects for      
films makes him oblivious to all the talking   
around him.As his family and friends struggle  
to cope up with his changing soundscape,       
Dr Swati tries to figure out the roots of      
his obsession and finally succeeds to identify.
Yet, Tarak plunges deeper and deeper into the  
world of the unheard as his love for cinema    
is unplugged.                                  



